            <p>The manuscript and proofs for her translation of Jenny Erpenbeck&apos;s <title render="italic">The Old child and
                other stories</title> are among the papers. Also present are drafts, proofs, etc. of her
                work <title render="italic">Foreign words: Translator-authors in the age of Goethe.</title></p>
        </scopecontent>

